    "created_at": "2016-05-11T08:47:16Z",
    "updated_at": "2016-05-11T10:39:53Z",
    "body": "While I agree with you, I'm not sure that it's in line with how other apps on Windows operate - most of Microsoft's apps would have both the X and the OK button, as an example.\n\n@zcbenz can make the call here - if he wants me to add an option to exclude the X, I can do that.\n"
